---
export interface Props {
  title: string;
}
const { title } = Astro.props;
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>{title} | Centros de Acopio Venezuela</title>
    <style>
      * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
      html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
      :root {
        --red: #CF142B;
        --red-dark: #A00F22;
        --blue: #00247D;
        --blue-dark: #001845;
        --yellow: #FFCC00;
        --gold: #D4A800;
        --bg: #F4F5F7;
        --card: #FFFFFF;
        --text: #1A1D23;
        --muted: #6B7280;
        --border: #E2E6ED;
        --radius: 12px;
      }
      body {
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
        background: var(--bg);
        color: var(--text);
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        line-height: 1.5;
        -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      }
      .flag-bar {
        display: flex;
        height: 6px;
      }
      .flag-bar span { flex: 1; }
      .flag-bar .y { background: var(--yellow); }
      .flag-bar .b { background: var(--blue); }
      .flag-bar .r { background: var(--red); }
      nav.navbar {
        position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100;
        background: var(--blue);
        color: white;
        padding: 0.65rem 1.25rem;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 0.75rem;
      }
      nav.navbar .brand-section {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        flex: 1;
      }
      nav.navbar .brand {
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        letter-spacing: -0.01em;
        line-height: 1.2;
      }
      nav.navbar .brand .sub {
        font-weight: 400;
        font-size: 0.7rem;
        opacity: 0.7;
        display: block;
      }
      nav.navbar .nav-emergencia {
        background: var(--red);
        color: white;
        padding: 0.4rem 0.9rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-size: 0.78rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: background 0.2s;
        white-space: nowrap;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
      }
      nav.navbar .nav-emergencia:hover { background: var(--red-dark); }
      header.hero {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue) 0%, var(--blue-dark) 60%, #001030 100%);
        color: white;
        padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem 3rem;
        text-align: center;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      header.hero .stars {
        position: absolute;
        top: 1.5rem;
        right: 1.5rem;
        font-size: 0.65rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.15em;
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
        user-select: none;
      }
      header.hero h1 {
        position: relative;
        font-size: 2rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        line-height: 1.15;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      }
      header.hero h1 span { color: var(--yellow); }
      header.hero p {
        position: relative;
        font-size: 0.92rem;
        opacity: 0.75;
        max-width: 460px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }
      header.hero p strong { opacity: 1; color: var(--yellow); font-weight: 600; }
      main {
        flex: 1;
        max-width: 1000px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem;
        width: 100%;
      }
      footer {
        background: #0F172A;
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
        text-align: center;
        padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem 2rem;
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        margin-top: auto;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      footer strong { color: white; font-weight: 600; }
      footer .flag-bar { max-width: 200px; margin: 0 auto 1.25rem; }
      footer .footer-top {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }
      footer .footer-top a {
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        transition: color .15s;
      }
      footer .footer-top a:hover { color: white; }
      footer .footer-top .ft-brand {
        color: white;
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      }
      footer .footer-top .ft-brand span { color: #FFCC00; }
      footer .footer-context {
        max-width: 560px;
        margin: 0 auto 1.25rem;
        font-size: 0.76rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
      }
      footer .footer-divider {
        width: 32px;
        height: 1px;
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
        margin: 0 auto 0.75rem;
      }
      footer .footer-end {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 0.4rem;
        font-size: 0.78rem;
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
      }
      footer .footer-end .heart { color: #CF142B; display: inline-block; }
      footer .footer-end strong { font-weight: 600; }
      footer .footer-links {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 0.6rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }
      footer .footer-links a {
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 0.74rem;
        padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
        border-radius: 6px;
        transition: all .15s;
      }
      footer .footer-links a:hover { color: white; border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2); }
      @media (max-width: 640px) {
        header.hero { padding: 1.5rem 1rem 2.25rem; }
        header.hero h1 { font-size: 1.5rem; }
        header.hero .stars { display: none; }
        main { padding: 1rem 0.75rem; }
        nav.navbar { padding: 0.5rem 0.85rem; }

      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="flag-bar"><span class="y"></span><span class="b"></span><span class="r"></span></div>
    <nav class="navbar">
      <div class="brand-section">
        <div class="brand">
          Centros de Acopio
          <span class="sub">Venezuela</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <a href="/emergencia" class="nav-emergencia">&#128222; Emergencia</a>
    </nav>
    <header class="hero">
      <div class="stars">&#9733; &#9733; &#9733; &#9733; &#9733; &#9733; &#9733; &#9733;</div>
      <h1>Centros de <span>Acopio</span> Venezuela</h1>
      <p>Ayuda a los afectados por el sismo del <strong>24 de junio de 2026</strong></p>
    </header>
    <main>
      <slot />
    </main>
    <footer>
      <div class="flag-bar"><span class="y"></span><span class="b"></span><span class="r"></span></div>
      <div class="footer-top">
        <span class="ft-brand">Centros de <span>Acopio</span></span>
        <a href="/">Inicio</a>
        <a href="/emergencia">Emergencia</a>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-context">
        El 24 de junio de 2026, dos sismos de magnitud 7.5 y 7.2 sacudieron la región central de Venezuela, afectando a Caracas, Miranda, La Guaira, Aragua y Carabobo. Esta plataforma centraliza los centros de acopio habilitados para recibir donaciones y ayudar a los damnificados.
      </div>
      <div class="footer-links">
        <a href="/">&#9733; Inicio</a>
        <a href="/emergencia">&#128222; Emergencia</a>

      </div>
      <div class="footer-divider"></div>
      <div class="footer-end">
        Hecho con <span class="heart">&#9829;</span> por la comunidad venezolana &mdash; <strong>Venezuela se levanta</strong>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
